@@$TJvSpeedButton
<TITLE TJvSpeedButton overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Buttons>
  TJvSpeedButton is an TSpeedButton ancestor that supports extended features such as hot tracking, and 
  can be associated with a pop-up menu.

  Set HotTrack to True, to provide visual feedback about when the button is under the mouse. 
  Use HotGlyph, HotTrackFont to alter the appearance of the Button when the mouse is over it.
  
  Use property HintColor to change the color of the hint boxes for the scroll bar.
  
  Assign a value to DropDownMenu to make a menu appear when the button is pressed. 
  
  ModalResult can be used as an easy way to make clicking the button close a modal form.
