@@TJvSpeedButton.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvSpeedButton object.
Description
  Use Create to create and initialize a new TJvSpeedButton object.
  
  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the speed button as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * HotTrack is set to False.
  * ModalResult is set to mrNone.  
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the speed button.
See Also
  Destroy, HintColor, HotTrack, ModalResult
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSpeedButton.Destroy
Summary
  Destroys an instance of TJvSpeedButton.
Description
  Do not call Destroy directly in an application. Instead, call Free. Free verifies that the 
  TJvSpeedButton object is not nil and only then calls Destroy.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
   Create
