@@TJvSpeedButton.Click
Summary
  Generates an OnClick event or triggers the associated action.
Description
  Calling Click generates an OnClick event, or triggers the associated action; Then, if ModalResult
  isn't equal to mrNone, it assigns the value of the button’s ModalResult property to the 
  ModalResult property of its parent form; Otherwise it checks if a pop-up menu is associated with 
  the button. If so, it pops up that pop-up menu.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
  DropDownMenu, ModalResult
