@@TJvSpeedButton.CMMouseEnter
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves over the speed button.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves over the speed button. It sets the
  hint color for the application to the property specified by HintColor; sets HotGlyph as the bitmap
  that shall appear on the button, if it's assigned; sets the font of the text on the button to 
  HotTrackFont if property HotTrack is true; and finally triggers the OnMouseEnter event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the speed button of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseLeave, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSpeedButton.CMMouseLeave
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves off the speed button.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves off the speed button. It resets the
  hint color for the application; resets the bitmap that shall appear on the buttom to the bitmap
  specified by Glyph; resets the font of the text on the button to Font; and finally triggers the
  OnMouseLeave event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the speed button of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseEnter, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
