@@TJvSpeedButton.CMParentColorChanged
Summary
  Responds when the color of the parent of the speed button changes.
Description
  CMParentColorChanged is called automatically when the color of the parent of the speed button changes.
  It triggers the OnParentColorChange event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the speed button of the parent
        color change.
